metadata.name: Wi Sa Ha
metadata.description:
" Wi Sa Ha " is a Thai word that means " When doing any action that encounters obstacles , risk of failure  , hard work but it can be done and tolerated."

My work is created by painting on a single layer from start to finish, no drafts, no filters. and no photo editing after that. 

Created on 14 April - 3 June

4608 x 6114 px
137 h 17 m
329,751  Stokes

The collector will get a split  the next artwork.
